item.title: Winner of the Inspirefest Ticket
item.description: Congratulations to Deardriu Lally on winnning the 2 complimentary tickets for Inspirefest at Bord GÃ¡is Energy Theatre, Grand Canal Square, Dublin 2. Inspirefest is a two day conference and takes place on the 30th June and 1st July. Inspirefest is a truly unique international festival of technology, science, design and the arts, which also happens to place diversity and inclusion at its heart. The event is an excellent opportunity to network with other companies and professionals, discuss the future of science and technology and to listen to key STEM speakers.
